^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Margaret should not like them playing 2@S. but she has no good bid and neither do I. Normally the person with shorter length in the opps suit should balance, but I have no good bid. With better clubs I might try 3@C and some players in Match Points might bid 3@H with Margaret's hand.|
