NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The bottom line is, balancing is done based on partnership assets, not just what you have in your hand. If they stop at the 2-level with a known 8-card fit, you are pretty sure the points are evenly spread, and you don't rate to get a good result if you let them play there.|
