^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Options over a takeout double
Redouble shows 10 or more. And most play 
2N shows a limit raise or better. (Some only play that over 1H or 1@S, but most play it over 1@C or 1@D also.)
2 level bids by advancer (me here) are weak, less than 10. So 2@C (or 2@H or 2@S) by me would be less than 10 points. Some less experienced players think 2@C by me shows 10+ points. That is incorrect. I would redouble with clubs and 10+.|
