NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|So if I bid 1@H or 1@S that is at most 9 and is not forcing. The reason I recommend that is it is less confusing. I think it is very counter intuitive that 1@H or 1@S by responder is potentially stronger than 2@C by responder. However, as I said most play that 1@H or 1@S, although they can and often are weak, can be stronger and are forcing.|
